# MLFQ Scheduling Expert (Healthcare)

ESI-mapped task priority management for Emergency Departments.

## 🏥 Triage Mapping ($K=5$)
- Q0: ESI 1 (Immediate)
- Q1: ESI 2 (Emergent)
- Q2: ESI 3 (Urgent)
- Q3: ESI 4 (Less Urgent)
- Q4: ESI 5 (Non-urgent)

## ⚙️ Starvation Prevention
- **Aging:** Move patients up if `wait_time > T_threshold`.

## Optimization
- Time Quantums per ESI level.
- Resource Allocation via AI.
